### Environment Variables
@authUrl = http://localhost:8080
@backendUrl = http://localhost:8000



### Get Own Portfolios - Success (with pagination)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Own Portfolios - Default Pagination
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Own Portfolios - Invalid Page (uses default)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own?page=0&limit=-5
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Own Portfolios - Unauthorized (401)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own

###

### Create Portfolio - Success
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My Investment Portfolio2",
  "description": "Tech stocks portfolio",
  "type": "stocks"
}

### Create Portfolio - Invalid Data (400)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": ""
}

### Create Portfolio - Unauthorized (401)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My Portfolio"
}

###

### Update Portfolio - Success
PUT {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own/id/{{portfolioId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Portfolio Title",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Update Portfolio - Invalid ID (400)
PUT {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own/id/invalid
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title"
}

### Update Portfolio - Not Found (404)
PUT {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own/id/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title"
}

### Update Portfolio - Unauthorized (401)
PUT {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own/id/{{portfolioId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title"
}

###

### Delete Portfolio - Success
DELETE {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own/id/{{portfolioId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Portfolio - Invalid ID (400)
DELETE {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own/id/invalid
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Portfolio - Not Found (404)
DELETE {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own/id/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Portfolio - Forbidden (not owner) (403)
DELETE {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own/id/{{portfolioId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete Portfolio - Unauthorized (401)
DELETE {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/own/id/{{portfolioId}}

###

### Get Portfolio by ID (Public) - Success
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/id/{{portfolioId}}

### Get Portfolio by ID (Public) - Invalid ID (400)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/id/invalid

### Get Portfolio by ID (Public) - Not Found (404)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/portfolios/id/99999
